cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with computer vision and image processing, specifically with inferring three-dimensional shapes from two-dimensional images. This falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also uses geometrical/topological invariants and machine learning techniques, which are relevant to graphics (cs.GR), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE).
